H0.text: What is the medical name for the breastbone. Xiphoid

H1.text: What is the medical name for the breastbone. Thorax

H2.text: What is the medical name for the breastbone. Costal

H3.text: What is the medical name for the breastbone. STERNUM

A4.text: The sternum (pl. : sternums or sterna) or breastbone is a long flat bone located in the central part of the chest.

A5.text: The sternum is a narrow, flat bone, forming the middle portion of the front of the chest.
